## 2. Advanced Search & Product Engine
Transitioning from matching raw strings to a structured product/variant hierarchy.

### Component: [Search Logic]
- [MODIFY] [db.ts](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/lib/db.ts):
    - **Normalization**: Trim whitespace, convert to lowercase, and remove special characters before querying.
    - **Global Search**: Update the header search to use a debounced search function that queries the "products" collection.
    - **Result Lists**: Ensure searching for "Stanley Cup" returns multiple items by using a keyword-based search (even if local filtering).

### Component: [Products Page]
- [MODIFY] [products/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/products/page.tsx):
    - Fix "Infinite Scanning": Add a timeout (e.g., 5s) that shows an error or "No results" if the fetch takes too long.
    - **Variant Support**: Update the Product interface to include `variantGroupId`. Products with the same ID will be grouped in the UI.

